Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.97,0:00:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Military Tribunal 54 ﻿is hereby convened.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.01,0:00:14.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.81,0:00:18.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That you lied to other countries about peace through neutrality
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.92,0:00:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿and developed grave threats, the Valvraves, in secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.53,0:00:25.87,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Do you have anything to say in your defense,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.87,0:00:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Prime Minister of Old JIOR, Sashinami Ryuji?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.70,0:00:35.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's the truth! It's delicious, you've got to try it!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.17,0:00:43.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Search results: zero. ﻿For that way of eating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.42,0:00:43.62,Alt,,0,0,0,,﻿Search results: zero. ﻿For that way of eating them.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.96,0:00:46.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll treat you when we get ﻿to the Moon, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.26,0:00:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Moon?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.38,0:00:50.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿On the Moon, I can get ﻿all the ingredients I mentioned.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.30,0:00:53.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Plus, the Moon is ﻿neutral territory.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.43,0:00:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The Dorssians won't be able to ﻿attack us anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.85,0:00:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The war will be ﻿over, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.43,0:01:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We'll go back to being ordinary students ﻿and focus on club activities.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.77,0:01:03.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We'll have proper ﻿classes, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.90,0:01:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿On Saturdays, we'll all go ﻿hang out together,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.15,0:01:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿and everything that was called off, ﻿we'll start up again.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.24,0:01:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't you worry! Once we get to the Moon, ﻿I know everything will be okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.54,0:03:10.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're late!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.59,0:03:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're the one ﻿who asked me to meet you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.70,0:03:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We were supposed to meet at 10, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:20.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Me getting here first is the same ﻿as you keeping me waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.45,0:03:21.79,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.79,0:03:22.87,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Fine, whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.17,0:03:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Miss Rukino. The reason ﻿I asked to meet you is—
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.67,0:03:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Miss Rukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.97,0:03:30.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're planning to talk ﻿on the sidewalk?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:41.85,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm at 90! ﻿Nobu Lightning, coming in!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.86,0:03:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Nobu-what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.61,0:03:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's this thing's name! "Unit 3" ﻿or whatever is lame, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.78,0:03:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I know! I know ﻿what you mean!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.47,0:04:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Okay, it looks like this will let you ﻿fight for extended periods.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.02,0:04:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Otamaya, ﻿how does Unit 1's—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.90,0:04:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Otamaya ﻿isn't here.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.77,0:04:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He left for the photo shoot. For the new cabinet.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:30.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿A minister... Minister... ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.43,0:04:32.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Me, a minister, can you believe it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.00,0:04:32.61,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\pos(240,29)\fs32\fad(220,0)}Minister of Culture & Science.\N﻿Yusuke Otamaya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.64,0:04:34.66,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\pos(960,35)\fad(300,0)}Minister of Land, Infrastructure,\N﻿Transport and Tourism:\NJuto Bansho
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.16,0:04:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Your tie's crooked.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.68,0:04:37.64,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\pos(246.038,24.5)\fs32\fad(220,0)}Minister of Finance.\N﻿Kyuma Inuzuka
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.01,0:04:37.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So sorry, my good ﻿Minister of Land & Transport.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:43.49,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\fad(250,0)\pos(153.962,87.5)}﻿Chief\NCabinet Secretary:\NSatomi Renbokoji﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.68,0:04:43.49,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\fad(250,0)\pos(1130.57,437)}Minister for\NForeign Affairs:\NTakahi Ninomiya
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.03,0:04:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Isn't that dress ﻿a bit daring?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:43.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I have to dress the part ﻿in order to associate with foreign countries.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.56,0:04:45.54,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\fad(250,0)\pos(205.283,29)}Minister of\NHealth and Welfare:\N﻿Rion Nanami
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.21,0:04:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Is everyone here?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.58,0:04:48.29,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\fad(250,250)\pos(990.189,32)}﻿Minister of Justice:\N﻿Iori Kitagawa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.66,0:04:49.32,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, Tokishima and Miss Rukino ﻿aren't here yet, and neither is—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.32,0:04:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sorry I'm late!
Comment: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿See? The "me" in "medamayaki" ﻿is a drawing of an eye!{"me" = eye, "medamayaki" = sunny-side-up fried eggs}
Comment: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.93,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fs32}"Me" = eye; "Medamayaki" = sunny-side-up fried eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.63,0:04:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿See? The "egg" for "sunny-side-up" ﻿is a manga eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.93,0:04:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Pretty sweet, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.89,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\fad(250,0)\pos(295.849,11)}﻿﻿Minister for Internal Affairs\Nand Communications:\NMarie Nobi
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.76,0:04:57.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If you want, we can all ﻿wear this shirt so we mat—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.40,0:04:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Vetoed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.40,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(1100,98)}﻿Prime Minister
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.31,0:05:00.40,Alt,,0,0,0,,{\fad(250,0)\pos(200,98)}Shoko Sashinami
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.23,0:05:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Um, Miss Rukino?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.90,0:05:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No! We said we'd talk ﻿after we got there.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.12,0:05:17.58,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿There it is! The one ﻿with the blue sign!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.58,0:05:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿There? But that's a place ﻿that serves alcohol!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.18,0:05:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.49,0:05:22.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're cabinet ministers now! ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.29,0:05:24.13,Default,,0,0,0,,We can just change the stupid law!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:33.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Flip this switch to the left... No, this can't be it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.05,0:05:36.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But these are ﻿the only switches...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.93,0:05:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, this is ﻿the one!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.35,0:05:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Ow! That's hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.90,0:05:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I refuse to let you apologize to me.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:05:58.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's weird, ﻿he's not picking up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.20,0:05:59.87,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Miss Rukino isn't ﻿here, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.87,0:06:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Wait, you don't think ﻿they're together, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.66,0:06:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Is that Haruto?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.30,0:06:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No, it's from ﻿another address.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:08.38,Alt,,0,0,0,,﻿"Congratulations,\N﻿Madam Prime Minister."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.76,0:06:13.88,Alt,,0,0,0,,﻿"Akira-chan,\N﻿thanks for the text!"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.09,0:06:13.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Akira-chan, ﻿thanks for the text!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.01,0:06:17.39,Alt,,0,0,0,,﻿"You’re welc—"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.71,0:06:36.26,Default,,0,0,0,,You're... welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:37.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I heard you!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.98,0:06:38.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.70,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,A friend! ﻿Akira Renbokoji!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:42.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Renbokoji?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.66,0:06:44.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! Why is my little sister calling you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.29,0:06:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll take care of anything she needs done ﻿outside, so I'll thank you to butt out.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.58,0:06:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, you have ﻿a little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:52.21,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Takahi, this is ﻿a personal matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.21,0:06:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Have any pictures?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.51,0:06:55.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Give it back, ﻿you girls!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.13,0:06:56.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}No way it's Shoko's phone.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.59,0:06:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Hi, here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.47,0:06:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is Rion Nanami ﻿the Health and Phys-Ed teacher.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.54,0:07:00.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I-It's nice to meet you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.88,0:07:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I-I'm on ﻿the student council with your brother!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.02,0:07:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm so sorry! ﻿I bet they spooked you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿We were all here taking the cabinet photo.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.53,0:07:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh, hey! Why don't you come join us?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The outside world is a lot of fun!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.15,0:07:12.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You'll make lots of new friends, too!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.73,0:07:15.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿You can eat cake with them ﻿go swimming with them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.74,0:07:17.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿It's for your own good, ﻿Akira-chan.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.99,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿You need to experience ﻿the outside world more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.50,0:07:31.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Akira-chan, ﻿please be our friend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.17,0:07:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.38,0:07:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No! No! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.08,0:07:40.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha— ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.25,0:07:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Akira-chan? ﻿Akira-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.25,0:07:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.27,0:07:53.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll go.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.12,0:07:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.80,0:07:56.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Akira is my sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.17,0:08:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've been alone ﻿my whole life.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.55,0:08:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Because no one ever chose me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Not my family, not my friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.80,0:08:21.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But they have!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.64,0:08:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You were a huge pop star, ﻿and were even in movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.39,0:08:29.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I wanted to be picked. ﻿If only by one person.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.85,0:08:34.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm all alone, so if I could be alone ﻿with someone else, that would be enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.15,0:08:37.65,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Miss Rukino... ﻿Are you talking about...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.12,0:08:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I've been alone ﻿my whole life.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.83,0:08:50.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Because no one ever chose me. ﻿{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.46,0:08:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Not my family not my friends.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:58.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Isn't that amazing? I did this movie ﻿two years ago, and I still remember my lines!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.38,0:09:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Turns out that I had a knack ﻿for acting, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.13,0:09:02.18,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.59,0:09:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You aren't alone, ﻿not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.44,0:09:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Enemy forces detected!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.86,0:09:23.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}All personnel, ﻿please go to level 1 battle alert!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.91,0:09:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Time's up, ﻿I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.29,0:09:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿They're between Module 77 ﻿and the Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.92,0:09:33.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿There's so many!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.26,0:09:35.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But we were ﻿almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:38.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We'll never reach the Moon ﻿without punching our way through them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.30,0:09:39.85,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We'll have to do ﻿just that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But how?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:47.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Watch team, report ﻿to the radar room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.41,0:09:51.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Air defense gun turrets will be set to debris ﻿shredding mode for this operation only.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.55,0:09:58.55,Alt,,0,0,0,,﻿"From: Satomi Renbokoji"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.59,0:10:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's unlike you to commit ﻿such a blunder, Capt. Cain.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.68,0:10:05.43,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿My apologies, sir.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.43,0:10:10.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿According to your report, those Valvraves have a limit ﻿to how long they can remain operational.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.23,0:10:12.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Yes, sir. If we ﻿press them en masse—{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.27,0:10:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.07,0:10:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿All we have to do is engage them ﻿in a protracted battle and exhaust them.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:20.82,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Module 77 is changing course ﻿to a heading of 741!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.82,0:10:21.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.49,0:10:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿They're running?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.04,0:10:28.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's the pragmatic ﻿choice. Nevertheless...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.91,0:10:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Understood, sir. ﻿We won't let them get away.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.50,0:10:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿All ships to maximum combat speed!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.03,0:10:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Commence pursuit battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.22,0:10:40.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dorssian fleet ﻿is pursuing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.05,0:10:42.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Maintain ﻿heading of 741.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.34,0:10:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Concentrate barrier system ﻿on our side facing the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:49.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.00,0:10:52.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Take up formation! ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.34,0:10:53.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Yamada, follow my lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.82,0:10:55.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's "Thunder"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.22,0:11:23.47,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Eat this! ﻿And this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.48,0:11:32.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dome block damaged ﻿through frame 277!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.02,0:11:35.31,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Barrier system ﻿output down to 87%!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.31,0:11:37.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿L-elf! There's just ﻿too many of them!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.86,0:11:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿We can't take ﻿much more of this!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.44,0:11:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've factored everything ﻿into my calculations.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.24,0:11:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The enemy fleet has utterly broken their ﻿formation in order to pursue Module 77.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.54,0:11:50.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, you're right! ﻿They're in a line now!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.66,0:11:55.08,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿In this formation, you can wipe them all out ﻿at once with your Harakiri Blade.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.08,0:11:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So that's why you ordered ﻿the course change!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.79,0:11:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It wasn't ﻿to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.26,0:12:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Your Harakiri Blade is the key ﻿to turning the tables.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.43,0:12:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If you miss your chance, this ﻿operation will end in failure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.80,0:12:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Understood.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.93,0:12:09.89,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Satomi Renbokoji.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.39,0:12:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.39,0:12:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've written out what will happen at each stage ﻿of the remainder of the operation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.19,0:12:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Give the orders ﻿as written here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.73,0:12:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Why me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.02,0:12:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿When it comes to talent for carrying out instructions ﻿written in a manual, you are the best there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.40,0:12:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What about you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.43,0:12:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You sound like ﻿you're going somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.16,0:12:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Secure transmission from Dorssian fleet!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.24,0:12:30.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿They want to speak with the Prime Minister!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.04,0:12:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.16,0:12:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shall I put it ﻿through?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.21,0:12:37.55,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yes. But in the Prime Minister's ﻿official residence.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.46,0:12:43.07,Default,,0,0,0,,You said "official residence"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.47,0:12:48.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're the prime minister of a country. I insist ﻿that you make the minimum effort to look the part.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.51,0:12:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Yeah. It's my turn ﻿this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.60,0:12:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿"This time"?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.06,0:13:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Until we got swept up ﻿in this war, I had no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.94,0:13:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I never knew how incredibly lucky ﻿we were to live in peace.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.95,0:13:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So I got to thinking that our peace didn't come free, ﻿and it's something that someone protected for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.87,0:13:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So now it's my turn ﻿to protect it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.75,0:13:22.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿A state's ultimate duty ﻿is the safety of its citizens.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.00,0:13:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's what ﻿Dorssia thought, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.09,0:13:27.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿As a result, they keep ﻿a massive military.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.18,0:13:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's not—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,You're patched through.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.64,0:13:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Dorssian Rear Admiral ﻿Delius Wartenberg.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.89,0:13:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko Sashinami, ﻿Prime Minister of JIOR.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.36,0:13:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿This is a time of war.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.65,0:13:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I'll dispense with the empty formalities.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.70,0:13:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.07,0:13:53.95,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The verdict of former JIOR Prime Minister ﻿Ryuji Sashinami's military tribunal was death.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.95,0:13:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.41,0:14:00.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I thought we told you that if you laid a hand on our families, ﻿we would hand over the Valvraves to ARUS!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Prepare to carry out ﻿the execution.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.13,0:14:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You cowards!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.63,0:14:08.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿To adults, that's ﻿a compliment.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.63,0:14:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Worrying about methods and ﻿aesthetics is a childish affectation.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.56,0:14:19.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Using any means, however dirty, to achieve ﻿one's objective is what an adult does.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.70,0:14:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Are you ﻿watching, Nobu?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.78,0:14:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You and me, we're gonna ﻿blow these guys to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.70,0:14:40.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿This is war. Victory glosses over ﻿any cowardice, any injustice.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.75,0:14:43.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've pinpointed ﻿the enemy's location.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.96,0:14:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The heart of the enemy fleet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.76,0:14:49.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's within the Harakiri Blade's firing range.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.51,0:14:50.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.35,0:14:58.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.52,0:15:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Now charging ﻿Harakiri Blade!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.15,0:15:02.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:06.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Haruto, my father ﻿is over there.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.86,0:15:11.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿If we let this chance pass us by, ﻿we'll be defeated.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.66,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I knew that you'd be ﻿coming at me from the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.13,0:15:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Carmilla is destroying ﻿enemy Waffen!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.05,0:15:34.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Enemy fleet speed ﻿increasing to 20!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.89,0:15:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Amazing... The battle is playing out ﻿exactly as L-elf wrote.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.68,0:15:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿What do I do? ﻿What should I do?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.27,0:15:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿The operation... ﻿The Valvraves...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.61,0:15:49.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿The war... ﻿The school...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Dad...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.66,0:15:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Think! ﻿Think, Shoko!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.03,0:15:59.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Another 26%. ﻿until he can fire.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.37,0:16:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Let's make a deal, ﻿my young Prime Minister.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.71,0:16:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿In exchange for the transfer ﻿of the Valvraves...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.48,0:16:10.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I will allow all of you students and ﻿your families to take asylum in a third-party country.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.72,0:16:12.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But that's—
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.56,0:16:14.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What about ﻿the other citizens of JIOR?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:16.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Abandon them.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.43,0:16:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿They're only the same race as you. ﻿{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.88,0:16:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}The vast majority are total strangers.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.39,0:16:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.42,0:16:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll never make ﻿a deal to save only ourselves!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.56,0:16:26.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿21% to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.11,0:16:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's a sad thing, ﻿being alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Safety and family.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That's ﻿more than enough to be happy.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.21,0:16:47.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Maybe so, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.63,0:16:50.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿You should leave the fighting to adults.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.65,0:16:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿You don't want your friends to die, do you?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.57,0:17:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿What's so funny?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.49,0:17:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿So it's you, Shoko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.88,0:17:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You're ﻿the new prime minister huh?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.03,0:17:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿The condemned isn't permitted ﻿to make an statements!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.12,0:17:22.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿What harm can it do ﻿for us to talk a little?{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.00,0:17:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿After all, this is a father's last ﻿conversation with his daughter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.58,0:17:28.29,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not the last! Don't give up so easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.29,0:17:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll save you, ﻿you hear me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.00,0:17:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Shut him up!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.00,0:17:35.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Stop that! ﻿Don't hurt my dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.39,0:17:45.10,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Their line is ﻿starting to scatter...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.10,0:17:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿How much longer ﻿for the Harakiri Blade?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.86,0:17:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Don't worry ﻿about me...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.94,0:17:57.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿It's an adult's job to return to the earth ﻿to make new flowers grow...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shut your mouth, ﻿you damn JIORan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.07,0:18:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dad!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.45,0:18:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Keep facing ﻿forward, Shoko.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.95,0:18:08.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Your future doesn't ﻿lie behind you!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.46,0:18:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Don't make me ﻿laugh, weakling!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.00,0:18:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dad!﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.83,0:18:13.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Another 3%...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.84,0:18:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.69,0:18:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm there!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.89,0:19:10.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He did it! ﻿Tokishima is so great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.19,0:19:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We can reach ﻿the Moon now!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.86,0:19:17.65,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Did ya see that, ﻿you Dorssian bastards?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.65,0:19:21.45,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Enemy fleet destruction ﻿confirmed at 74%!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.20,0:19:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Now! Charge through the hole we've opened ﻿in their middle and make for the Moon!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.27,0:19:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I couldn't... ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.50,0:19:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,do anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.19,0:19:36.56,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.08,0:19:57.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Everything went ﻿according to your plan, L-elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.36,0:19:59.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿How far ahead ﻿can you see?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.50,0:20:01.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿He can't see ﻿anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.47,0:20:05.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Object closing in ﻿at high speed from below!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿From below?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.39,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.77,0:20:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿A-An Ideal-class has—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.53,0:20:28.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The pit's wrecked! ﻿The Valvraves can't get back in!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.24,0:20:30.10,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We can't cool them off now, ﻿either!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.10,0:20:31.78,Default,,0,0,0,,What are we gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.59,0:20:40.79,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.79,0:20:41.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Don't!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.88,0:20:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Professor!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.01,0:20:50.39,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿H-neun. ﻿The drill is yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.39,0:20:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Blitzendegen!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.18,0:20:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We're being boarded ﻿by the enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.85,0:20:57.52,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Mr. President, ﻿we need orders!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.52,0:20:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿G-Give me ﻿a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.23,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's not in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.40,0:21:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing ﻿about this written in here, damn it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.41,0:21:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We'll just pull ﻿the damn thing out, then!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.91,0:21:14.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Valvraves.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.99,0:21:17.29,Default,,0,0,0,,We're going to ﻿settle things once and for all.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.13,0:21:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Miss Rukino, take me back ﻿to Module 77!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.34,0:21:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Unit 1 can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:28.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I know! I'll fight ﻿them hand to hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:37.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Now sealing all bulkheads ﻿below level B4!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.73,0:21:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I repeat, now sealing ﻿all bulkheads below level B4!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿Annihilate the enemy after ﻿luring them into position.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.45,0:21:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿I'm happy to see you following ﻿my training so scrupulously.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.50,0:22:00.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}﻿However, that makes you ﻿easy to predict.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.84,0:22:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll come back when ﻿my Valvrave has cooled off!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.59,0:22:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Do your best ﻿to rescue Shoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.39,0:22:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Wait! Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.69,0:22:23.48,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Idiot, what do you think ﻿you're doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.48,0:22:27.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've been thinking about ﻿what will happen after this battle is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.45,0:22:31.61,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Saki Rukino...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.61,0:22:33.17,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Will you...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.17,0:22:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,marry me?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:13.59,0:24:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Next time, episode 12, ﻿"The Heretic Activates”.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.51,0:24:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Valvrave the Liberator...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.38,0:24:24.06,Default,,0,0,0,,The system that will ﻿expose the truth of the world.
